how to know the audience size

To know the audience size, you can create a custom audience by uploading a CSV file with user identifiers like email addresses or device IDs. Once the platform matches this data with its user database, it generates a custom audience segment. You can then view and manage your audience size through the Audience Management tool. For more details, check out our guide on Audience Management here: [Introduction to Audience Management](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/26679465558669-Introduction-to-Audience-Management).
